<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">

<head>

  <meta charset="UTF-8" />

  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>

  <title>Portfolio Layout</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>

  <style>

    * {

      margin: 0;

      padding: 0;

      box-sizing: border-box;

    }

    body {

      font-family: Georgia, serif;

      background: #2f2f2f;

      color: black;

      display: flex;

      justify-content: center;

      padding: 40px;

    }

    .page {

      width: 1100px;

      background: #f5f5f5;

      padding: 32px;

      border: 2px solid black;

    }

    /* NAV */

    nav {

      display: flex;

      justify-content: space-between;

      align-items: center;

      margin-bottom: 40px;

    }

    .logo {
      font-family: Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: black;
    }

    .nav-links {

      display: flex;

      gap: 32px;

      font-size: 18px;

    }

    .nav-links a {

      text-decoration: none;

      color: black;

    }

    /* HERO */

    .divider {

      border-top: 1px solid #999;

      margin-bottom: 50px;

    }

    .hero h1 {

      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 5.5rem);

      line-height: 1;

      max-width: 1000px;

      font-weight: 700;

      margin-bottom: 32px;

    }

    .hero p {

      max-width: 850px;

      font-size: 1rem;

      line-height: 1.6;

      margin-bottom: 80px;

    }

    /* PROJECT GRID */

    .projects {

      display: grid;

      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);

      gap: 48px 32px;

    }

    .project-card {

      width: 100%;

    }

    .project-image {

      width: 100%;

      aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;

      background: #cfcfcf;

      border: 2px solid #3b82f6;

      position: relative;

      overflow: hidden;

      margin-bottom: 14px;

    }

    .project-image::before,

    .project-image::after {

      content: "";

      position: absolute;

      width: 140%;

      height: 2px;

      background: #3b82f6;

      top: 50%;

      left: -20%;

    }

    .project-image::before {

      transform: rotate(25deg);

    }

    .project-image::after {

      transform: rotate(-25deg);

    }

    .project-client {

      font-size: 0.85rem;

      margin-bottom: 6px;

    }

    .project-title {

      font-size: 2rem;

      font-weight: bold;

      margin-bottom: 8px;

    }

    .project-meta {

      font-size: 0.9rem;

      color: #333;

    }

    /* RESPONSIVE */

    @media (max-width: 800px) {

      .projects {

        grid-template-columns: 1fr;

      }

      nav {

        flex-direction: column;

        align-items: flex-start;

        gap: 20px;

      }

      .hero h1 {

        font-size: 3rem;

      }

    }

  </style>

</head>

<body>

  <div class="page">

    <nav>

      <div class="logo">Amanda Ross</div>

      <div class="nav-links">

        <a href="#">Work</a>

        <a href="#">About</a>

      </div>

    </nav>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <section class="hero">

      <h1>

        Volupta voluptas pisci neserunt que dit quunt remolor ectatusci quam et quatiis eos dolorehent adio to volorunt quia quo ipsanda musaese quibus.

      </h1>

      <p>

        Xere vo roribu? Gia piciatem eos et am, tem faccus sitaturem voloreniham fuga.

        Sed que restis aut aliguidem, ipi aute et tus nobis maio cus, sun est,

        ut quiat accus, nonseque evel mod untis non porem cum fuga.

      </p>

    </section>

    <section class="projects">

      <div class="project-card">

        <div class="project-image"></div>

        <div class="project-client">Who is your client?</div>

        <div class="project-title">Title of Project</div>

        <div class="project-meta">

          Category, type, or project

        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="project-card">

        <div class="project-image"></div>

        <div class="project-client">Who is your client?</div>

        <div class="project-title">Title of Project</div>

        <div class="project-meta">

          Category, type, or project

        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="project-card">

        <div class="project-image"></div>

        <div class="project-client">Who is your client?</div>

        <div class="project-title">Title of Project</div>

        <div class="project-meta">

          Category, type, or project

        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="project-card">

        <div class="project-image"></div>

        <div class="project-client">Who is your client?</div>

        <div class="project-title">Title of Project</div>

        <div class="project-meta">

          Category, type, or project

        </div>

      </div>

    </section>

  </div>

</body>

</html>